Android RC App

Visual:
	Pitch and Roll - Control with motion sensors
	Yall - Joystick or Buttons	|=> Righthand side
	Throthle - Joystick or Buttons	|
	
	Control ON button => Lefthand side
		ON states sets the control trough the phone. When OFF - automatic control. (pitch and roll - default = 0, yall and throthle - 			default=last)
	2 functional buttons
	
	Textfield - battery status

Communication:
	UDP
	



 
